                <note rend="inline" type="source">816.01/390: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Minister in Costa Rica</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Sack</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1934-01-22T17:00:00-05:00"
                            >January 22, 1934—5 p.m.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>3. Your 4, January 22, 2 p.m. Inasmuch as we have not recognized the Salvadoran
                    Government it would not be appropriate for you to accept.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Hull</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
